            <who name="Fabian Jakobs">fabian.jakobs</who>
            <bug_when>2008-05-30 11:51:09 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>In 0.8 we support the capturing event phase. This allows us to add a capturing listener to handle activation. The &quot;normal&quot; bubbling listeners can then safely be stopped.</thetext>
